  "title": "Admin Assistant (Office Hours, 5 Days, No Experience Required – Training Provided) #HJG",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Provide administrative support including filing, data entry, and document management</li><li>Assist in scheduling appointments and managing calendars</li><li>Handle basic correspondence and communication with internal teams</li><li>Maintain records and update databases accurately</li><li>Support day-to-day office operations to ensure smooth workflow</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Min GCE ‘N’/‘O’ Levels, ‘A’ Levels, Diploma and above</li><li>Keen interest in the healthcare/medical industry</li><li>No experience needed, full training will be provided</li><li>Basic knowledge of Microsoft Office</li><li>Able to start work immediately</li></ul><p>If you are interested in this position, do kindly drop your most updated resume to joshua.gan@recruitexpress.com.sg and leonleong@recruitexpress.com.sg (Attn: Admin Assistant)</p><p><br /></p><p>Leon Leong De Cong<br />R1551708<br />Recruit Express Pte Ltd (Healthcare & Lifesciences Division)<br />EA License: 99C4599</p>",
